693
01:01:31,105 --> 01:01:34,483
<i>The world stood still forth at stolen kiss.</i>

694
01:01:34,859 --> 01:01:37,111
<i>And as he grew, so did the technology.</i>

695
01:01:37,194 --> 01:01:39,280
<i>An entire human life</i>

