738
01:03:47,074 --> 01:03:48,200
Truman!

739
01:03:48,283 --> 01:03:49,576
Truman, no!

740
01:03:50,577 --> 01:03:51,745
That's off-limits.

741
01:03:51,829 --> 01:03:55,541
- Why? What's over there?
